@startuml
title LowCortisol WebApp - Support Frontend Bounded Context Layers
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
hide circle

package "Support Frontend Bounded Context" {
  class "Domain" as Frontend_service_management_Domain <<layer>>
  class "Application" as Frontend_service_management_Application <<layer>>
  class "Infrastructure" as Frontend_service_management_Infrastructure <<layer>>
  class "Presentation" as Frontend_service_management_Presentation <<layer>>
}

Frontend_service_management_Presentation ..> Frontend_service_management_Application : user actions / state
Frontend_service_management_Application ..> Frontend_service_management_Domain : models and rules
Frontend_service_management_Application ..> Frontend_service_management_Infrastructure : API services / adapters
Frontend_service_management_Infrastructure ..> Frontend_service_management_Domain : resources and mappers
Frontend_service_management_Presentation ..> Frontend_service_management_Domain : view models

note bottom of Frontend_service_management_Application
Detailed class diagrams for each layer are available in docs/diagrams/class/frontend/layers/support.
end note

@enduml
